title: Gabriela Kratochvílová
text:
Gabriela Lašková (<a href="Given%20name">née</a> Kratochvílová; born 11 February 1990) is a Czech model and anchor who was crowned <a href="Czech%20Miss">Czech Miss 2013</a> and represented <a href="Czech%20Republic">Czech Republic</a> at <a href="Miss%20Universe%202013">Miss Universe 2013</a>. Since 2014 she is an anchor of the main news program on the Czech TV station <a href="Prima%20televize">Prima</a>.
Miss Universe Czech Republic.
The ninth edition of the Czech Miss beauty contest was held on 23 March 2013 at the Karlín Musical Theatre. Throughout the evening ten finalists performed in traditional disciplines such as a swimsuit walk, but also in non-traditional disciplines of the competition that they had performed during a camp in the Philippines.
